SELECT "January", "February", "March", "April", "May", "June", "July" ,"August" ,"September" ,"October" ,"November" ,"December" 
FROM CROSSTAB(
	$$
		SELECT CD."Category" AS "rowid", M."Month" AS "category", COALESCE(CD."Demand", 0) AS "value"
		FROM (SELECT GENERATE_SERIES AS "Month"  FROM GENERATE_SERIES(1,12)) M
		LEFT JOIN "CategoryDemand" CD ON CD."Month" = M."Month" AND CD."Category" = 'Amazon Devices'
		ORDER BY M."Month"
	$$,
	$$ 
		SELECT * FROM GENERATE_SERIES(1, 12)
	$$) AS 
	FINAL_RESULT(
		"Category" TEXT, "January" NUMERIC, "February" NUMERIC, "March" NUMERIC, "April" NUMERIC, "May" NUMERIC, "June" NUMERIC,
		"July" NUMERIC, "August" NUMERIC, "September" NUMERIC, "October" NUMERIC, "November" NUMERIC, "December" NUMERIC)

SELECT TO_CHAR(TO_TIMESTAMP("Date", 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'Month') AS "Month", "Demand"
FROM (
	SELECT CONCAT('2020-', "Month", '-01') AS "Date", "Demand"
	FROM "CategoryDemand"
	WHERE "Category" = 'All Electronics'
	ORDER BY "Demand" DESC
	LIMIT 1) T
